content: standujar: Focused on enhancing streaming support across multiple plugins and the core Eliza application, opening four significant feature PRs including elizaos-plugins/plugin-anthropic#12, elizaos-plugins/plugin-openrouter#21, elizaos-plugins/plugin-openai#21, and elizaos/eliza#6212, demonstrating a primary focus on feature work with substantial code changes across 799 files (+30195/-9717 lines).
